---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Course" description="Course information for Ngawi Golf Club — a links course on the Wairarapa Coast.">

  <!-- Mini-hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[320px] flex items-end">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center"
      style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587174486073-ae5e5cff23aa?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')"
    ></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, oklch(0.21 0.055 160 / 0.85) 0%, oklch(0.21 0.055 160 / 0.35) 55%, transparent 100%)"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12 w-full">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-tight">The Course</h1>
      <p class="text-white/75 text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
        Links golf on the Palliser Bay coast — wild, windswept, and unlike anywhere else in New Zealand.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Details + Rules -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <div class="bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] mb-6">Course Details</h2>
        <dl class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-border text-sm">
          {[
            ['Holes', '9'],
            ['Par', '36'],
            ['Type', 'Links'],
            ['Location', 'Ngawi, Wairarapa'],
            ['Green Fee', '$10 NZD'],
          ].map(([label, value]) => (
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5">
              <dt class="text-muted-foreground">{label}</dt>
              <dd class="font-medium text-foreground">{value}</dd>
            </div>
          ))}
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] mb-6">Course Rules</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-foreground">
          {['Have fun', 'Be respectful', 'If the ball goes over the road….'].map(rule => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[oklch(0.527_0.136_150)] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                <path d="M3 8l3.5 3.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
              {rule}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] mb-3">Getting Here</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5 max-w-2xl">
        Ngawi is located at the southern tip of the Wairarapa, approximately 2.5 hours from Wellington via Martinborough and Palliser Bay.
        Follow State Highway 53 through Lake Ferry — Ngawi is at the end of the road, right on the coast.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Ngawi+Golf+Club+Wairarapa"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-[oklch(0.448_0.119_154)] hover:text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] transition-colors"
      >
        View on Google Maps →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <div class="pb-16">
    <div
      class="flex overflow-x-auto"
      style="scroll-snap-type: x mandatory; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; scrollbar-width: none;"
    >
      {[
        { id: 'photo-1553284965-83fd3e82fa5a', alt: 'Links golf landscape' },
        { id: 'photo-1596727147705-61a532a659bd', alt: 'Coastal golf views' },
        { id: 'photo-1591491683301-8ef31e8976f2', alt: 'Golfer on the course' },
        { id: 'photo-1587174486073-ae5e5cff23aa', alt: 'Golf course fairway' },
        { id: 'photo-1535131749006-b7f58c99034b', alt: 'Golfer teeing off' },
      ].map(({ id, alt }) => (
        <img
          src={`https://images.unsplash.com/${id}?q=80&w=700&auto=format&fit=crop`}
          alt={alt}
          class="h-56 md:h-80 w-[75vw] md:w-[520px] flex-shrink-0 object-cover"
          style="scroll-snap-align: start;"
        />
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- History & Community -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] mb-8">History &amp; Community</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <p>
          Ngawi Golf Club has been part of this rugged coastal community for generations. Founded by locals who wanted a place to play, unwind, and connect, the club has always been about more than golf — it's a gathering point for the people of Ngawi and the wider Palliser Bay region.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ngawi itself is one of New Zealand's most distinctive fishing villages, known for its fleet of bulldozers used to launch boats straight off the beach into the surf. Sitting at the foot of Cape Palliser, the southernmost point of the North Island, the area is wild, windswept, and unlike anywhere else in the country.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <p>
          The golf course reflects that character — unpretentious, memorable, and deeply tied to the land. Whether you're a local who's played every hole a hundred times, or a traveller making the journey down SH53 for the first time, you'll find a warm welcome and a round worth remembering.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA band -->
  <section class="bg-[oklch(0.964_0.015_145)] border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-14 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] mb-1">Ready to play?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Green fees from $10 NZD. No booking required.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/fees" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[oklch(0.296_0.083_156)] hover:bg-[oklch(0.25_0.07_156)] active:scale-95 text-white font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 rounded-xl transition-all text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
        View Fees &amp; Pay →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
